由于肯塔基州恶劣天气，第二届《杀手重聚》演出被取消https://www.nme.com/news/music/second-slayer-reunion-show-cancelled-due-to-bad-weather-in-kentucky-3798048?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=second-slayer-reunion-由于肯塔基州恶劣天气取消演出Emma WilkesSun, 29 Sep 2024 16:01:47 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3798048 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杀手" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该乐队最近在 Riot Fest 上重聚，这是他们五年来的首场演出</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/second-slayer-reunion-show-cancelled-due-to-bad-weather-in-kentucky-3798048">由于肯塔基州恶劣天气而取消的《第二杀手》重聚节目</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杀手" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/slayer-scott-dudelson-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于极端天气， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slayer">Slayer</a>在肯塔基州 Louder Than Life 音乐节上的第二场重聚演出已被取消。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/slayer-film-the-repentless-killology-is-vulgar-gruesome-and-problematic-just-like-the-band-2574276"><b>杀手电影《无悔的杀戮学》粗俗、可怕且有问题——就像乐队一样</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>Slayer 不太可能的回归在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayer-reunite-and-announce-first-live-shows-in-five-years-3590923">今年早些时候得到了证实</a>，当时有消息称他们将成为两个 9 月音乐节的主角——芝加哥的 Riot Fest（22 号）和肯塔基州路易斯维尔的 Louder Than Life 音乐节（27 号）。</p><p>他们在 Riot Fest 上的演出标志着鞭打金属传奇人物自漫长的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayer-announce-final-dates-of-farewell-tour-2526467">告别世界巡演</a>结束以来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-slayer-played-at-their-first-live-gig-in-five-years-3796054">近五年来的首次现场演出</a>。该乐队在芝加哥音乐节上演奏了一系列最受欢迎的歌曲，其中包括《Raining Blood》、《Angel Of Death》和《South Of Heaven》，贯穿他们的 20 首主打歌曲。</p><p>然而，由于天气问题，他们在肯塔基州 Louder Than Life Festival 上举行的第二场演出不得不取消。由于飓风海伦（美国有史以来最严重的风暴之一）的余波，出于安全原因，整个第二天的活动不得不取消。</p><p> Louder Than Life 组织者在一份声明中表示：“Louder Family，我们很伤心地分享这件事，但今天的天气对我们不利。我们一直在与气象学家和地方当局密切合作，抱着能够打开大门的希望，但持续的阵风使我们无法安全前进。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAcB7axBgEf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" bac